  "keyFeatures": [
    "Scrum, Waterfall, and Kanban project management methodologies",
    "Integrated bug tracking with lifecycle management",
    "Quality assurance with test cases, test suites, and test reports",
    "Product and story management with review workflows",
    "DevOps integration with Git, GitLab, Gitea, Jenkins, and CI/CD pipelines",
    "REST API v1 and v2 for external integrations",
    "Extension system for custom functionality",
    "Multi-language support (zh-cn, zh-tw, en, de, fr)",
    "Business intelligence, metrics, and reporting dashboards",
    "Document and knowledge base management"
